eria}}\n| [[Nigeria]]<ref name=punchng1 />\n| [[Goodluck Jonathan]]<ref name=\"macleans_arrive\"/>\n| [[President of Nigeria|President]]\n|-\n! {{flagicon|Spain}}\n| [[Spain]]<ref name = \"pm_canada\"/>\n| [[Jos\u00e9 Luis Rodr\u00edguez Zapatero]]<ref name=\"razon\">{{cite news| title=Zapatero pide ante los l\u00edderes de la cumbre imponer \"deberes\" a los mercados| work=[[La Raz\u00f3n (Madrid)|La Raz\u00f3n]]| location=[[Madrid]]| date=27 June 2010| language=Spanish| publisher=larazon.es}}</ref>\n| [[Prime Minister of Spain|Prime Minister]]\n|-\n! {{flagicon|Vietnam}}\n| [[Vietnam]]<ref name = \"pm_canada\"/>\n| [[Nguyen Tan Dung]]<ref name=\"lin\"/>\n| [[Prime Minister of Vietnam|Prime Minister]]<ref>2010 Chair of [[ASEAN]]</ref>\n|-  style=\"background:#ccc; text-align:center;\"\n! colspan=\"4\" style=\"background: LightSteelBlue;\"|International organizations\n|-  style=\"background:#ccc; text-align:center;\"\n! colspan=2 | Organization\n! Represented by\n! Title\n|-\n! <!--Please do not add the flag of the African Union, since it is copyrighted-->\n| [[African Union]]\n| [[Bingu wa Mutharika]]<ref name=\"macleans_arrive\"/><ref name=\"dailystar\">{{cite news| url=http://www.thedailystar.net/newDesign/news-details.php?nid=145223| title=Rich man, poor man| work=The Daily Star| location=[[Dhaka]]| date=4 July 2010| publisher=dailystar.net| author=Mahmood Hasan| accessdate=2012-03-26| url-status=live| archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121023192031/http://www.thedailystar.net/newDesign/news-details.php?nid=145223| archivedate=23 October 2012}}</ref><ref name=\"whittington\">{{cite news| author=Les Whittington and Bruce Campion-Smith| title=G20 set to tackle sharp differences over economic policy| url=https://www.thestar.com/news/gta/torontog20summit/article/828930--g20-set-to-tackle-sharp-differences-over-economic-policy| work=Toronto Star| date=25 June 2010| publisher=thestar.com| accessdate=2012-03-26| url-status=live| archiveurl=https://web.archive.org