-replace-emily-blunt-in-iron-man-2/|archive-date=August 29, 2012|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Avengers\">{{cite web|url=https://www.deadline.com/2010/07/star-wattage-marvel-assembles-the-avengers-for-comic-con-panel|title=Marvel-ous Star Wattage: Actors Assemble For Comic-Con Panel Including 'The Avengers', 'Captain America', & 'Thor{{'-}}|date=July 24, 2010|author=<!-- The Deadline Team-->|work=[[Deadline Hollywood]]|access-date=July 25, 2010|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/5zx6k1EnB?url=http://www.deadline.com/2010/07/star-wattage-marvel-assembles-the-avengers-for-comic-con-panel#|archive-date=July 5, 2011|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"WinterSoldier\">{{cite web|url=https://www.deadline.com/2012/10/five-actresses-testing-for-captain-america-2-role-black-widow-might-drop-by-as-well//|title=Five Actresses Testing For 'Captain America 2\u2032 Role; Black Widow Might Drop By As Well|first=Mike|last=Fleming Jr.|work=[[Deadline Hollywood]]|date=October 2, 2012|access-date=October 2, 2012|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121004165957/http://www.deadline.com/2012/10/five-actresses-testing-for-captain-america-2-role-black-widow-might-drop-by-as-well/|archive-date=October 4, 2012|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"AvengersAoU\">{{cite web|url=http://www.nydailynews.com/entertainment/gossip/scarlett-johansson-flaunts-curves-new-magazine-photo-shoot-article-1.1470378|title=Scarlett Johansson flaunts curves in new magazine photo shoot, reveals details on 'The Avengers' sequel|last=Maresca|first=Rachel|work=[[New York Daily News]]|date=September 29, 2013|access-date=September 29, 2013|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130929050049/http://www.nydailynews.com/entertainment/gossip/scarlett-johansson-flaunts-curves-new-magazine-photo-shoot-article-1.1470378|archive-date=September 29, 2013|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"IGNSep2010\">{{cite web|url=https://www.ign.com/articles/2010/09/22/black-widow-the-movie|title=Black Widow: 