ie|website=[[Collider (website)|Collider]]|date=January 14, 2020|access-date=January 16, 2020|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200115153419/https://collider.com/alexandre-desplat-black-widow-composer/|archive-date=January 15, 2020|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Beristain\">{{cite web|url=https://collider.com/black-widow-cinematographer-gabriel-beristain/|title='Black Widow' Cinematographer Mystery Solved: Gabriel Beristain Shot the Marvel Movie|last=Sneider|first=Jeff|website=[[Collider (website)|Collider]]|date=January 16, 2020|access-date=January 17, 2020|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200117183524/https://collider.com/black-widow-cinematographer-gabriel-beristain/|archive-date=January 17, 2020|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Synopsis\">{{cite web|url=https://comicbook.com/marvel/2020/01/14/marvel-black-widow-movie-synopsis-story-details/|title=Marvel Releases New Black Widow Synopsis|last=Outlaw|first=Kofi|website=ComicBook.com|date=January 14, 2020|access-date=February 11, 2020|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200115170045/https://comicbook.com/marvel/2020/01/14/marvel-black-widow-movie-synopsis-story-details/|archive-date=February 11, 2020|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"PolygonFinalTrailer\">{{cite web|url=https://www.polygon.com/2020/3/9/21171352/black-widow-final-trailer-taskmaster-marvel-studios-release-may-1|title=Marvel's final Black Widow trailer 'goes back to the beginning'|last=Carpenter|first=Nicole|website=[[Polygon (website)|Polygon]]|date=March 9, 2020|access-date=March 9, 2020|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200309170706/https://www.polygon.com/2020/3/9/21171352/black-widow-final-trailer-taskmaster-marvel-studios-release-may-1|archive-date=March 9, 2020|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"TaskmasterFinalTrailer\">{{cite web|url=https://www.slashfilm.com/final-black-widow-trailer/|title='Black Widow' Trailer: Natasha Romanoff Made Some Bad Decisions Before She Became an Avenger|last=An